{"tid":707570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人出街好驚撞到ex","createTime":"2018-06-18T17:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T09:09:03.000Z","uid":94309,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06c555141c6f4f869f2d2e685975c0b9626e5b9a","tid":707570,"uid":94309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"佢同新囝個幾月了<br />\n去啲佢有機會去既地方<br />\n一ff到會見到佢同新囝<br />\n就會好緊張 周圍望 睇下見唔見<br />\n行得好快 周圍避 兜路行<br />\n個心跳得好快咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我認我好廢 但比之前好好多了<br />\n對自己好左 諗少左佢 冇同佢聯絡 但都仲會咁<br />\n有冇人都會咁 定係得我咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43ef488f565ad087526b4a6a91004dec47b381d","tid":707570,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"驚驚下就無咗件事"},{"pid":"0939066b10ad020a1aade276ccc6604a92e0b5de","tid":707570,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"一收工即返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b4812b6bb833831079d183d1467b125cc932bc","tid":707570,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:25:45.000Z","msg":"果陣分左一排會 撞到直情跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後係街撞到都冇野<br />\n而家好耐冇見"},{"pid":"0edd6a7c6798e89abe7d85631ff0995da098bedf","tid":707570,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T19:44:14.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"ed293c5f715a8f7b361df56f24c2d17fb7ee95bc","tid":707570,"uid":3643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T20:13:01.000Z","msg":"會 自己仲要單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39442019f52f05671d3833e9ddaaaf6bb046c07","tid":707570,"uid":94309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"去親啲佢會去既地方<br />\n成條街啲女人都好似係佢咁<br />\n好辛苦囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/